 17LIVE引入了“插图V模式”，该功能允许通过单个插图进行虚拟分配，并且可以调整眼睛、嘴巴和头部的运动范围。 https://www.moguravr.com/17live-illustration-vtuber/ノンジャンル人生 Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:36:51 +0000 VTuberイチナナhttps://www.moguravr.com/?p=250253 <p>直播应用程序“17LIVE（Ichinana）”引入了“插画V模式”，该功能使您只需在应用程序中注册单个插图即可轻松进行虚拟直播。到目前为止，“17LIVE”已经使用Live2D [...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/17live-illustration-vtuber/">17LIVE 后引入了“插图 V 模式”，该功能允许通过单个插图进行虚拟分发。可以调整眼睛、嘴巴和头部的运动范围，这</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>直播应用程序<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://jp.17.live/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>17LIVE（Ichinana）</strong></a> <strong>”</strong>引入了<strong>“插画V模式”，</strong>该功能使您只需在应用程序中注册单个插图即可轻松进行虚拟直播。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.e8t0z5muq1xb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.e8t0z5muq1xb-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.e8t0z5muq1xb-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.e8t0z5muq1xb-300x157.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.e8t0z5muq1xb-768x402.webp 768w" width="1000" height="523" /></a></p><p>迄今为止，“17LIVE”在进行虚拟分发时需要Live2D模型等专用模型。随着这项新功能的推出，即使是那些觉得自己想作为 V Liver 进行直播，但准备模型似乎很困难的人，现在也可以通过简单的操作享受虚拟直播。</p><p>为了纪念本次“图鉴V模式”功能的上线，我们还将开展支持V肝首发的活动。活动期间，凡报名成为“认证V肝”并连续7天以上进行1小时以上直播的用户，将获赠价值10,000日元的亚马逊礼券（其他成就条件适用）。活动持续至6月30日（周日）。</p><p>点击此处了解详情。<br /> <a href="https://jp.17.live/news/32601/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://jp.17.live/news/32601/</a></p><h2>如何开始</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.avrkc658qs74-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.avrkc658qs74-493x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.avrkc658qs74-493x1024.webp 493w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.avrkc658qs74-145x300.webp 145w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.avrkc658qs74-jpg.webp 500w" width="493" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.dry9hbe9sghe-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.dry9hbe9sghe-493x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.dry9hbe9sghe-493x1024.webp 493w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.dry9hbe9sghe-145x300.webp 145w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.dry9hbe9sghe-jpg.webp 500w" width="493" height="1024" /></a></p><p>要使用“插画V模式”，请先选择“插画V模式”并上传您自己的插画。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.bde4ujhk57w-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.bde4ujhk57w-493x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.bde4ujhk57w-493x1024.webp 493w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.bde4ujhk57w-145x300.webp 145w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/a59fc5972122c697ba0ff4dfc29002c6-kix.bde4ujhk57w-jpg.webp 500w" width="493" height="1024" /